Hi Alan,
The AT16 has been superceeded with the AT-Fast/PCI-Fast cards. The Linux
drivers will only be for the AT-Fast/PCI-Fast range of cards. We have not
had much luck with the drivers for the old AT and AT+ cards under Linux.
Regards,
Hugh Anderson
